video.title: LEGO Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu
video.synopsis: Kai, Jay, Cole and Zane must master their elemental powers and Spinjitzu weapons to protect the land of Ninjago, which also has an underworld.

episodes.synopsis: The ninjas are snapped out of their post-hero complacency when Lord Garmadon's son Lloyd shows up and tries to pick up where his father left off.
episodes.title: Rise of the Snakes

episodes.synopsis: Back in training mode with the looming threat of Lloyd and the Hypnobrai, Zane wanders after a Falcon and lands himself in a heap of trouble.
episodes.title: Home

episodes.synopsis: Lloyd unlocks a second tribe, the Fangpyres, to help him regain control. The ninjas take action when the Fangpyres attack Jay's family's village.
episodes.title: Snakebit

episodes.synopsis: After the Fangpyres join forces with the Hypnobrai, Lloyd awakens Pythor -- the last remaining snake of the Anacondrai tribe.
episodes.title: Never Trust a Snake

episodes.synopsis: Lloyd moves in and tries to help out but just gets in the way. Pythor awakens the Venomari and the Constrictai, and an all-out snake war breaks out.
episodes.title: Can of Worms

episodes.synopsis: Pythor declares himself the destined leader who'll reawaken The Great Devourer, an ancient beast that can't be killed and will consume all of Ninjago.
episodes.title: The Snake King

episodes.synopsis: When the four ninjas follow the mysterious falcon into the woods, they stumble upon a hidden workshop where Zane learns the secret about his past.
episodes.title: Tick Tock

episodes.synopsis: Jay and Nya must cut short their first date in Mega-Monster Amusement Park as the Serpentine are on their way to retrieve one of four fang blades.
episodes.title: Once Bitten, Twice Shy

episodes.synopsis: The ninjas go undercover as a dance troupe and enter a talent contest in their quest to win the Blade Cup, where one of the fang blades is hidden.
episodes.title: The Royal Blacksmiths

episodes.synopsis: The ninjas are suspicious when their archenemy Lord Garmadon moves in to help search for his missing son, but they realize they have to work together.
episodes.title: The Green Ninja

episodes.synopsis: The ninjas try to infiltrate the Serpentines' inner sanctum and walk into a trap. When Lloyd's rescue mission fails, only Lord Garmadon can help.
episodes.title: All of Nothing

episodes.synopsis: The ninjas hastily journey to the lost city of Ouroboros to try to stop Pythor from awakening The Great Devourer, but it's a race against time.
episodes.title: Rise of the Great Devourer

episodes.synopsis: Disaster threatens as the ninjas must fight to defeat the all-consuming Great Devourer in a desperate attempt to save Ninjago.
episodes.title: Day of the Great Devourer

episodes.synopsis: Just as the rebuilding effort in Ninjago begins, the four ninjas realize Lord Garmadon has forged the ninjas' lost Golden Weapons into a mega-weapon.
episodes.title: Darkness Shall Rise

episodes.synopsis: When Garmadon accidentally brings to life the ruthless Captain Soto and his pirates, it's up to the ninjas to stop them from plundering Ninjago City.
episodes.title: Pirates vs. Ninja

episodes.synopsis: When our heroes are invited back to Darkly's Boarding School, they discover it's a trap set up by Lord Garmadon and his evil replica ninjas.
episodes.title: Double Trouble

episodes.synopsis: When the ninjas learn Darreth's Mojo Dojo is to be destroyed, they enter the annual NinjaBall Run to win a cash prize that will help save the dojo.
episodes.title: Ninjaball Run

episodes.synopsis: When the ninjas prevent Garmadon from using his mega-weapon to bring to life a fossilized monster, they're turned into kids and need Lloyd's help.
episodes.title: Child's Play

episodes.synopsis: When Garmadon travels back in time to undo the past and rid the future of ninjas, the ninjas follow him and try to stop him using the Golden Weapons.
episodes.title: Wrong Place, Wrong Time

episodes.synopsis: The ninjas face off with an exhibit of a stone samurai warrior that the toxic venom from the Great Devourer has brought to life.
episodes.title: The Stone Army

episodes.synopsis: The ninjas try to flee from the Stone Army, which has been brought to life by the Devourer's toxic venom. Garmadon tries to seize control of the army.
episodes.title: The Day Ninjago Stood Still

episodes.synopsis: The ninjas, Lloyd, Sensei Wu and Misako journey to the Dark Island to find a Temple of Light that can restore the ninjas' elemental powers.
episodes.title: The Last Voyage

episodes.synopsis: After fighting off the Stone Army, the ninjas arrive at the Temple of Light and harness their pure elemental powers, concentrating them onto Lloyd.
episodes.title: Island of Darkness

episodes.synopsis: The ninjas try to return Garmadon's Helmet of Darkness to its perch at the Celestial Clock to prevent the final battle between Lloyd and his father.
episodes.title: The Last Hope

episodes.synopsis: Garmadon uses his new super-weapon to turn Jamanakai Village evil, unsettling the balance and allowing the spirit of the Overlord to possess his body.
episodes.title: Return of the Overlord

episodes.synopsis: A great darkness has fallen upon Ninjago as Garmadon's super-weapon has turned it evil, but the ninjas discover light is more powerful than dark.
episodes.title: Rise of the Spinjitzu Master

episodes.synopsis: In the wake of Overlord's defeat, Ninjago City is reborn and the ninjas teach at Sensei Wu's academy. But the peace doesn't last long.
episodes.title: The Surge

episodes.synopsis: After being pursued to Sensei Garmadon's monastery by the Nindroids, the ninjas sneak back into Ninjago City under the guise of a circus train.
episodes.title: The Art of the Silent Fist

episodes.synopsis: Zane gives up half his power to save P.I.X.A.L. just as foes attack from all sides. Meanwhile, Lloyd and his father travel to Hiroshi's Labyrinth.
episodes.title: Blackout

episodes.synopsis: Underneath Ninjago City, the ninjas discover secrets about the Serpentine when they fight alongside them against the Nindroids.
episodes.title: The Curse of the Golden Master

episodes.synopsis: The ninjas venture into the Digiverse to confront the Digital Overlord. Meanwhile, Pythor and Wu lead a Nindroid attack on Borg Tower.
episodes.title: Enter the Digiverse

episodes.synopsis: Pythor and the Nindroids free the Digital Overlord. Meanwhile, Wu and Garmadon stumble upon Pythor's top-secret scheme, Project Arcturus.
episodes.title: Codename: Arcturus

episodes.synopsis: After battling Nindroids on the outside of the Arcturus ship, the ninjas hang on as the craft takes the battle into the heart of a comet.
episodes.title: The Void

episodes.synopsis: The Nindroids use the Golden Weapons to transform the Overlord into the Golden Master. In the ruins of Ninjago, the ninjas prepare their final stand.
episodes.title: The Titanium Ninja

episodes.synopsis: After discovering that Zane may still be alive, the ninjas learn that they must compete in a Tournament of Elements if they wish to see him again.
episodes.title: The Invitation

episodes.synopsis: The team learns about Jade Blades and other secrets of the Tournament of Elements. Karlof is eliminated from the competition.
episodes.title: Only One Can Remain

episodes.synopsis: The contests begin, and soon Cole is forced to battle with Jay. Zane regains his memory with help from P.I.X.A.L.
episodes.title: Versus

episodes.synopsis: The remaining Elemental Masters compete in a roller skating competition. Cole, Karlof and other eliminations must work in Chen's noodle factory.
episodes.title: Ninja Roll

episodes.synopsis: The ninjas form an alliance with the Elemental Masters after revealing Chen's plan. Cole and Zane break out of the noodle factory.
episodes.title: Spy for a Spy

episodes.synopsis: Lloyd and Garmadon learn of the great battle that once took place between Chen, the Anacondrai and the Elemental Masters for control of Ninjago.
episodes.title: Spellbound

episodes.synopsis: It appears that all is lost when Chen drains the powers of the Elemental Masters and vanquishes Lloyd in battle to take control of his as well.
episodes.title: The Forgotten Element

episodes.synopsis: Chen and his army invade Ninjago City, but the masters have escaped the noodle factory and follow close behind. Garmadon narrowly escapes banishment.
episodes.title: Day of the Dragon

episodes.synopsis: Master Chen uses a spell to turn himself and his troops into fierce Anacondrai, but the ninjas visit Ninjago City's jail to recruit an unusual ally.
episodes.title: The Greatest Fear of All

episodes.synopsis: The final confrontation between the ninjas and the Anacondrai unfolds, but a great sacrifice must be made if the heroes are to save the day.
episodes.title: The Corridor of Elders

episodes.synopsis: Morro possesses Lloyd and uses him to infiltrate the tea shop and attack the other ninjas, who have mysteriously lost their powers.
episodes.title: Winds of Change

episodes.synopsis: After learning that Wu's staff holds a clue to the First Spinjitzu Master's tomb, the ninjas go to Stiix to retrieve the stolen Airjitzu scroll.
episodes.title: Ghost Story

episodes.synopsis: While Wu trains Nya in her new water powers, the ninjas plot to steal the Airjitzu scrolls from Ronin but find that they must first fight Morro.
episodes.title: Stiix & Stones

episodes.synopsis: The ninjas go to Sensei Yang's dangerous haunted temple to learn Airjitzu, and Nya quits her training but must use her powers to elude Morro's ghosts.
episodes.title: The Temple on Haunted Hill

episodes.synopsis: Using their new Airjitzu powers, the ninjas race to climb a perilous mountain to find the Sword of Sanctuary before Morro can claim it.
episodes.title: Peak-a-Boo

episodes.synopsis: After being betrayed in the Cloud Kingdom, the ninjas battle Morro for the Sword of Sanctuary and learn he is ultimately after the Realm Crystal.
episodes.title: Kingdom Come

episodes.synopsis: As the ninjas close in on their final clue to the location of the First Spinjitzu Master's tomb, Ronin steals the Sword of Sanctuary to give to Morro.
episodes.title: The Crooked Path

episodes.synopsis: The ninjas journey to the First Spinjitzu Master's tomb to claim the powerful Realm Crystal, but they must navigate a series of traps -- and Morro.
episodes.title: Grave Danger

episodes.synopsis: As the ninjas race to keep Morro from releasing the Preeminent, Morro uses the Realm Crystal to summon an army of ghosts from the Cursed Realm.
episodes.title: Curse World: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: While the ninjas try to protect Stiix, Lloyd encounters his father in the Cursed Realm, and Nya unlocks her true potential to take on the Preeminent.
episodes.title: Curse World: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: The ninjas find themselves going from famous heroes to hunted villains when someone impersonates them and commits crimes all over Ninjago City.
episodes.title: Infamous

episodes.synopsis: While Nadakhan schemes to steal the Realm Crystal, the fugitive ninjas are pursued by Ronin, who has been hired by the police to track them down.
episodes.title: Public Enemy Number One

episodes.synopsis: Falsely imprisoned, the ninjas meet a fellow captive who knows of a rare venom that can stop a Djinn like Nadakhan, but it's only found on one island.
episodes.title: Enkrypted

episodes.synopsis: Nadakhan talks Jay into making a wish to win over Nya, first mate Flintlocke accidentally destroys the Realm Crystal, and Cole steals Soto's map.
episodes.title: Misfortune Rising

episodes.synopsis: As large areas of Ninjago City vanish, the ninjas head to Tiger Widow Island, where Jay collects the precious venom with Nadakhan in hot pursuit.
episodes.title: On a Wish and a Prayer

episodes.synopsis: Marooned on Tiger Widow Island, Lloyd, Cole and Nya try to escape on a raft, while a captured Jay battles Nadakhan's crewmates for their amusement.
episodes.title: My Dinner with Nadakhan

episodes.synopsis: After lessons in how to talk like pirates, the ninjas infiltrate Nadakhan's ship on a mission to slip him the venom and rescue Jay from captivity.
episodes.title: Wishmasters

episodes.synopsis: Flintlocke leads a mutiny, believing Nadakhan will abandon his crew once he has the power of infinite wishes, but the Djinn prevails and captures Nya.
episodes.title: The Last Resort

episodes.synopsis: While Nya is forced to rehearse for her wedding to Nadakhan at the Djinn Temple, Jay recruits a new team for a mission to rescue his friends.
episodes.title: Operation Land Ho!

episodes.synopsis: Nadakhan marries Nya and gains the power of infinite wishes, but Flintlocke and Dogshank join the ninjas to fight the Djinn in an epic final showdown.
episodes.title: The Way Back

episodes.synopsis: Master Wu engages in a fight left unfinished decades ago against Acronix, one of the twin Hands of Time. The ninjas try to rescue him.
episodes.title: The Hands of Time

episodes.synopsis: The ninjas learn more about fallen Elemental Masters, Krux and Acronix, and discover they have a new enemy.
episodes.title: The Hatching

episodes.synopsis: Kai uses a Vermillion Warrior helmet to uncover information about Krux, while Lloyd struggles as a master-in-training and Nya tries to reboot Zane.
episodes.title: A Time of Traitors

episodes.synopsis: The Vermillion Warriors mysteriously steal items made of metal while Lloyd comes to realize that filling Master Wu's shoes is a daunting task.
episodes.title: Scavengers

episodes.synopsis: The ninjas fight to save an amusement park while Jay defends his family home from the Vermillion Warriors -- until the Emerald Time Blade arrives.
episodes.title: A Line in the Sand

episodes.synopsis: The team enjoys a victory and retrieves the Emerald Time Blade, but the celebration is short-lived.
episodes.title: The Attack

episodes.synopsis: While the rest of the ninjas try to find and rescue Master Wu, Nya confronts the Samurai X imposter and Kai seeks the truth about his parents.
episodes.title: Secrets Discovered

episodes.synopsis: Kai discovers both of his parents are being held captive. Meanwhile, a third Time Blade appears.
episodes.title: Pause and Effect

episodes.synopsis: The Hands of Time force Kai and Nya into retrieving the fourth Time Blade from the Boiling Sea.
episodes.title: Out of the Fire and Into the Boiling Sea

episodes.synopsis: Kai and Nya time travel to the past, where they must help the Elemental Masters prevent the Hands of Time from changing Ninjago history.
episodes.title: Lost in Time

episodes.synopsis: After he loses the Mask of Deception to a new villain, Lloyd reunites the scattered ninjas.
episodes.title: The Mask of Deception

episodes.synopsis: Lloyd befriends the spirited Princess Harumi, but an explosive attack by the Sons of Garmadon results in another relic lost and her parents missing.
episodes.title: The Jade Princess

episodes.synopsis: The ninjas seek the Sons of Garmadon by interrogating a captured gang member and going undercover at a karaoke bar.
episodes.title: The Oni and the Dragon

episodes.synopsis: Zane is taken to the Sons of Garmadon's secret base, where he learns about their unseen leader. Meanwhile, Lloyd discovers the gang's true purpose.
episodes.title: Snake Jaguar

episodes.synopsis: Zane and Mr. E meet in an epic face-off as the ninjas' ship embarks on a rocky journey to find the third Oni mask.
episodes.title: Dead Man's Squall

episodes.synopsis: Separated by the crash, the ninjas try to get to the Oni mask before the Sons of Garmadon.
episodes.title: The Quiet One

episodes.synopsis: A flashback reveals the truth about the Quiet One's identity as Harumi and Lloyd venture deeper into the Oni Temple seeking the third mask.
episodes.title: Game of Masks

episodes.synopsis: Lloyd awakens a prisoner of the Quiet One, who plans to resurrect Lord Garmadon with another hostage.
episodes.title: Dread On Arrival

episodes.synopsis: The ninjas celebrate at Laughy's until they learn Garmadon has broken Harumi out of prison.
episodes.title: True Potential

episodes.synopsis: Mystake heals Lloyd's injuries but his survival comes with a heavy price. Garmadon conjures up a destructive giant to display his powers.
episodes.title: Big Trouble, Little Ninjago

episodes.synopsis: Lloyd hides from the occupying forces of Emperor Garmadon and Harumi, while Young Wu and the ninjas are marooned in the Realm of Oni and Dragon.
episodes.title: Firstbourne

episodes.synopsis: Iron Baron banishes Jay, Kai and Zane to doom in an arena against a dragon. In Ninjago, Lloyd assembles a rebel group of Elemental Fighters.
episodes.title: Iron & Stone

episodes.synopsis: The ninjas are caged and used as bait to lure a dragon. Lloyd and his resistance fighters hijack a TV station to broadcast a message of hope.
episodes.title: Radio Free Ninjago

episodes.synopsis: The enslaved ninjas gather materials so that Cole and Wu can build a dragon decoy. The Sons of Garmadon strike back at Lloyd's rebels.
episodes.title: How to Build a Dragon

episodes.synopsis: Lloyd and some of the resistance fighters are on the brink of capture in Nya's vehicle. In the Realm of Oni and Dragon, the ninjas and Wu go on the run.
episodes.title: The Gilded Path

episodes.synopsis: Mystake reveals her true nature and past, while Wu leads the search for Firstbourne.
episodes.title: Two Lies, One Truth

episodes.synopsis: Wu's identity is revealed while Lloyd and his comrades come up with a new plan involving Harumi.
episodes.title: The Weakest Link

episodes.synopsis: When Wu is captured and electro-shocked, his memories suddenly return. Lloyd uses stolen powers to try and seize the Oni Titan.
episodes.title: Saving Faith

episodes.synopsis: An angry Garmadon looks to regain control while Wu and Iron Baron land in Firstbourne's nest.
episodes.title: Lessons for a Master

episodes.synopsis: The ninjas return to Ninjago and head to battle just as a terrible attack is underway while Master Wu and Lloyd confront Lord Garmadon.
episodes.title: Green Destiny

episodes.synopsis: Faith arrives with news of an invasion, forcing Lloyd to consider making Lord Garmadon an ally.
episodes.title: The Darkness Comes

episodes.synopsis: Despite their grave doubts, the ninjas free Lord Garmadon from Kryptarium Prison so that he and Lloyd can enter the cloud of darkness.
episodes.title: Into The Breach

episodes.synopsis: The team pays a terrible price when they attempt to rescue Lloyd and Lord Garmadon, who discover the Oni's weakness while battling the Omega.
episodes.title: The Fall

episodes.synopsis: The ninjas race back to the Monastery of Spinjitzu, where they must combine their powers and make their last stand against the Oni.
episodes.title: Endings
